== Geometric hatch ==

[[Image:TechDraw_GeometricHatch.svg|16px]] [[TechDraw_GeometricHatch|TechDraw GeometricHatch]] forms a pattern of lines based on a specification read from a file.  This file is generally compatible with the widely used AutoDeskÂ® PAT format.  A small selection of patterns is included in the FCPAT.pat file:

